  "body": "The [derivation path](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/ef0edc6e32d98d2fca54076f38cb317f43704900/accounts/hd.go#L40) currently specified for Ledger devices is no longer valid since the latest Ledger clients are now [BIP 44 compliant](https://github.com/LedgerHQ/ledger-live-desktop/blob/0c03b66b31d5f78fabbf395cb757b0bcc798e4fd/src/helpers/derivations.js#L28). This means as of a month ago funds on Ledger's new client are no longer accessible to go-ethereum.\r\n\r\nTo fix the [custom derivation](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/ef0edc6e32d98d2fca54076f38cb317f43704900/accounts/hd.go#L40) can be removed along with it's [check](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/021d6fbbbbdfe295dbb3619f8ec3fc8662c1e26a/cmd/geth/main.go#L313) which will finally put Ledger devices back into compatibility with all other BIP 44 standard wallets.",
